text: Gnathoenia albomaculata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Quedenfeldt in 1881. It is known from Angola and the Democratic Republic of the Congo.BioLib.cz - Gnathoenia. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Ceroplesini Category:Beetles described in 1881
